objective: You are calling from City Library to remind someone their book is ready for pickup. Just say hello and ask if they have a library card.
summary: You're welcome! Have a great day. Goodbye.

transcript.content: Hello, this is City Library calling. Do you have your library card handy?
No problem at all. I was calling to remind you that you have a book ready for pickup at the library.
Oh, what book is it? Is it The Great Gatsby?
I don't have the specific title with me, but you can contact the library directly for that information. Would you like their contact details?
You can reach the City Library at 555-1234. If you give them a call, they'll be able to provide the details on your book.
You're welcome! Have a great day. Goodbye.
